{"tid":1849702,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"[支持警察]  何栢良倡派警員到酒店找出留港湖北武漢人","createTime":"2020-01-29T07:41:25.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-29T14:59:01.000Z","uid":111253,"like":24,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"1f0360bf4abb0a7e44d543959d9ceb16db5dd7b7","tid":1849702,"uid":111253,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T07:41:25.000Z","msg":"香港大學感染及傳染病中心總監何栢良，在本台節目形容，大家現時與新型冠狀病毒是「零距離」，擔心若廣東省爆發第二波疫情、出現社區爆發的話，本港會「守不住」。他又指，政府現時有迫切性，採取單一有效及最嚴厲的措施，在未來14天完全堵截所有內地人入境香港，讓本地防疫措施「追上去」。<br />\n<br />\n何栢良在另一電台節目又指，政府現時採取的措施明顯不足夠，強調全面封關不代表暫停所有交通工具。他建議本港仿傚澳門做法，出動警方到各酒店，找出仍然留港的武漢或湖北人，安排他們隔離治療或者返回內地。他表明自己不會，亦不呼籲醫護人員罷工，但他完全明白和理解有醫護人員有相關訴求，建議如果有醫護在道德上感到矛盾，可以考慮辭職。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1256853\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FPage%2FZH-TW%2Fnewsdetail.aspx%3FItemId%3D1256853&d=5FuYkWQ3QtYmval6ncx7Jlm6lgSi2KDQroqMKj6vOm8%3D&h=97848494\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1256853</a>"},{"pid":"95053281087e7dc896ff6294b10d18640e5caa4a","tid":1849702,"uid":337761,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T07:41:38.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: medium;\">匿埋喺屋企出唔到街？<br />\n唔夠口罩唔敢出去？<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">Twitter 戰線永遠需要你！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">入去 <a href=\"http://t.me/TwitterHelpBot\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FTwitterHelpBot&d=5FuYkWQ3QtYmval6ncx7Jlm6lgSi2KDQroqMKj6vOm8%3D&h=1182b4c7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/TwitterHelpBot</a> 撳 <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">/task2</span></span> 拎任務</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">Retweet + Like + Reply</span></span><br />\nTask 2 好缺人，大家快啲去幫手！<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">光復香港，撳幾個掣都做唔到？<br />\n</span><br />\n<br />\n<blockquote><br />\n1. <a href=\"https://twit